# =============================================================================
# .dockerignore - 告訴 Docker「這些檔案不要複製進去」
# .dockerignore - Tell Docker "don't copy these files"
# =============================================================================
# 作用類似 .gitignore，但是針對 docker build 時的 COPY 指令
# Similar to .gitignore, but for the COPY command during docker build
#
# 好處 Benefits：
#   1. 減少 Image 大小 / Reduce image size
#   2. 避免把機密資訊（如 .env）打包進去 / Prevent secrets (like .env) from being included
#   3. 加快 build 速度 / Speed up build time
# =============================================================================

# Python 虛擬環境 - 容器會自己安裝，不需要複製
# Python virtual environment - container will install its own, no need to copy
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# 環境變數（機密資訊！）
# Environment variables (secrets!)
.env

# Git 資料夾 / Git folder
.git/
.gitignore

# IDE 設定 / IDE settings
.vscode/
.idea/

# macOS 系統檔案 / macOS system files
.DS_Store

# Postman 測試檔案（不需要在 production 環境）
# Postman test files (not needed in production)
postman/

# 文件（不影響程式執行）
# Documentation (doesn't affect program execution)
docs/
README.md
*.md